title: Zelenskyy reports good results from SBU in countering Russian operations
text:
Zelenskyy reports good results from SBU in countering Russian operations
Kyiv¬†‚Ä¢¬†UNN
President Zelenskyy heard a report from the First Deputy Head of the SBU, Oleksandr Poklad. He noted the SBU's good results in countering Russian operations against Ukraine and its citizens.
President of Ukraine Volodymyr Zelenskyy heard a report from the First Deputy Head of the SBU, Oleksandr Poklad. The head of state announced this on Telegram, writes UNN.
There are good results from the Security Service of Ukraine in countering Russian operations against our state, our people. Oleksandr reported on the details of the Service's work in neutralizing threats from Russia.
Zelenskyy also thanked SBU employees, everyone who thwarts enemy plans and thus protects the country.
"Every such result strengthens us in diplomacy and in bringing about a reliable peace," Zelenskyy added.
